headline: Here's the 1 Stock Warren Buffett Bought in 2024 He's Most Likely to Buy Again This Quarter
summary: It's no secret that Warren Buffett isn't finding many stocks he likes enough to buy these days.  Which stock did Buffett buy in 2024 that he's most likely to buy again this quarter?  The most notable addition to Berkshire Hathaway's portfolio in the first quarter of 2024 was Chubb (NYSE: CB).

headline: Is 2025 the Year to Buy Warren Buffett's 3 Worst-Performing Stocks of the Past Decade?
summary: Warren Buffett will likely go down as the greatest investor of all time -- and he recently proved just how good he is even at 94 years old.  In a last-minute comeback, Buffett's company Berkshire Hathaway beat the broader benchmark S&P 500 yet again in 2024.  Berkshire has now beaten the broader market in three of the last four years.
